AUDIO: 'various tools, check out this video here that I did earlier. Of course, the main benefit of having this MIDI data is now we can convert it into as many different voices as we want to. Why don\'t we go ahead and stick with Rebecca and let\'s hear what she sounds like right now in this form and not in pre-recorded'

